      <title>英国赤字上升给财政大臣预算出台带来压力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/uk-records-higher-borrowing-than-expected-in-first-six-months</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国本财年上半年的政府赤字大于预期，这加大了财政大臣雷切尔·里夫斯（Rachel Reeves）的压力，迫使她提高税收并增加借款以在下周的预算中弥补更高的支出。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-10-22/uk-records-higher-borrowing-than-expected-in-first-six-months</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 22 Oct 2024 06:15:45 GMT</pubDate>
